local-bench

This repository includes frozen benchmark item sets derived from:

- MMLU-Pro by TIGER-Lab, distributed under the MIT License.
- IFBench_test by AllenAI/Ai2, dataset license ODC-BY-1.0.
- IFEval by Google Research, distributed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.

The following source is used by a candidate axis (Math, Coding-exec, and Agentic
axes carry 0% weight in the headline Index and are under validation):

- Berkeley Function-Calling Leaderboard (BFCL) by Gorilla LLM / UC Berkeley,
  distributed under the Apache License, Version 2.0. Berkeley-derived items and
  evaluation patterns inform the Agentic candidate axis.

The IFEval checker registry and scoring behavior in
cli/src/localbench/scorers/ifeval/ are adapted from the Google Research
instruction_following_eval implementation (Apache-2.0). Note the distinction for
IFBench: the IFBench_test dataset is redistributed under ODC-BY-1.0, while the
Ai2 IFBench verifier *code* (and the IFEval-style verifier patterns reused here)
are Apache-2.0.

Full third-party license texts are in the LICENSES/ directory. A per-dataset
redistribution analysis is in docs/foundations/license-inventory-v1.md. The
license for local-bench's own source code is not yet finalized; see the top-level
LICENSE file.
